    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for perfection? This car is in truly mint condition and feels like it just left the showroom! Every inch of this vehicle has been meticulously cared for, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior. It drives beautifully and offers a like-new experience for its next owner. This is a rare find for anyone seeking excellence!",
